Michael Szabados, MBA

Age : 64Public asset : 1,519,448 USDLinked companies :  NetScout Systems, Inc. 





Summary 



Mr. Michael Szabados is Chief Operating Officer at NetScout Systems, Inc.Mr. Szabados was previously employed as Vice President-Product Management by UB Networks, a Director-Product Marketing by Bay Networks, Inc., a Director-Product Marketing by Synoptics, Inc., and Marketing Director by Miller Information Processing Services Corp.He received his undergraduate degree from the University of California, Irvine and an MBA from Santa Clara University.



